<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-advance-of">in advance (of )</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>提前 (于…)；预先 (于…)；超前于：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Thank you in advance.
先行致谢。</p><footer>2013 全国书面表达</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When students were told my rule in advance of the class, some of them were not happy.
当学生们在课前得知我的规矩后，他们中的一些人感到不快。</p><footer>2011 北京</footer></div></div>